OL,3,CSeven people and two firms charged
OL,4,Cover Hong Kong fire that killed 168
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FHong Kong officials have charged seven
OL,8,Fpeople and two companies with offences
OL,9,Fincluding manslaughter and conspiracy
OL,10,Fover last year's fire, which killed
OL,11,F168 people.
OL,13,FThe fire, which broke out on November
OL,14,F26 2025, engulfed seven blocks of
OL,15,Fflats in Hong Kong's Tai Po district.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
