OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781089373
OL,3,CSeven people and two firms charged
OL,4,Cover Hong Kong fire that killed 168
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FFormer residents and relatives of the
OL,8,Fvictims have spent months waiting for
OL,9,Fanswers after the blaze tore through
OL,10,Fthe close-knit Wang Fuk Court housing
OL,11,Festate, which was home to thousands of
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FIn a statement on Wednesday, local
OL,15,Fauthorities said police and the
OL,16,FIndependent Commission Against
OL,17,FCorruption charged the suspects with
OL,18,F25 counts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
