OL,3,CSeven people and two firms charged
OL,4,Cover Hong Kong fire that killed 168
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FThe allegations also include money
OL,8,Flaundering, attempting to pervert the
OL,9,Fcourse of justice, and tax evasion.
OL,11,FAuthorities said the seven people held
OL,12,Fdifferent roles in the major
OL,13,Frenovation project at Wang Fuk Court.
OL,15,FThe two companies charged are the
OL,16,Fproject consultancy firm and the main
OL,17,Fcontractor involved in the works.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
