OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIn March, police said they arrested 38
OL,13,Fpeople on suspicion of offences linked
OL,14,Fto the complex, including manslaughter
OL,15,Fand fraud, with nine later charged.
OL,17,FIn the same month, the Independent
OL,18,FCommission Against Corruption said it
OL,19,Fhad also arrested 23 people on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of offences including
OL,21,Fbribery and conspiracy to defraud.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
